# This is the TODO File. Things here might appear in future versions of the bot.

- Add a level-up system
  - Messages make you level up
  - 1 Msg = 10 XP, every 5 minutes
  - Every level = 500 XP
  - Add other ways to get XP
  - Ranks
    - Point: Lv 1 - 5
    - Segment: Lv 6 - 10
    - Ray: Lv 11 - 15
    - Line: Lv 16 - 20
    - Triangle: Lv 21 - 30
    - Square: Lv 31 - 40
    - Hexagon: Lv 41 - 50
    - Tetrahedron: Lv 51 - 65
    - Prism: Lv 66 - 80
    - Octahedron: Lv 81 - 95
    - Dodecahedron: Lv 96 - 110
    - Icosahedron: Lv 111 - 125
    - Hyperprism: Lv 126+
- Add a mana system
  - 3 types of mana
    - Primal mana
      - Regenerates over time
      - Obtained with messages
    - Crystal mana
      - Obtained with messages
    - Power mana
      - Obtained with lv up
    - Void mana
      - Obtained only with void charms
  - Typing minigame will grant all 3 types of mana
  - Users can cast charms that do funny Things
  - Charms may include
    - Blind: User cannot read text channels
      - 5 Minute duration
      - 1 Hour cooldown (5 Minutes if voided)
    - Drain: Remove 25% of someone else's mana
      - 1 Hour cooldown (None if voided)
    - Distraction: The bot (and any other sasuke-helper instances) begins typing
      - 15 Minute duration
      - 1 Hour cooldown (None if voided)
    - Void: Turn server into anarchy server, begin production of void mana
      - Cannot be used if already voided

    - Drone strikes
      - 1 Hour cooldown (15 minutes if voided)
    - Mana stream: Provides an infinite amount of Primal mana for a duration
      - 1 Hour duration (infinite if voided)
      - 6 Hour cooldown
    - Freeze: Commit full mute on a members
      - 5 Minute duration
      - 1 Hour cooldown (5 Minutes if voided)
    
    - Restore: Removes debuffs (blind, freeze) on a user
      - 1 Hour cooldown (only if voided)
    - Music: Playing music
      - If voided, instead does funny
    - Poison: Decrease the audio quality of a channel
      - Cannot be used if voided

    - Clean: Cleaning webhooks
      - Cannot be used if voided
    - Funny: Ban people for void mana
      - Only if voided
- Switch codebase to typescript